---
const VIDEO_ID = 'EAwDdmpl-GQ';
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-navy-900 py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-teal-500 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-gold-400/40 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-12">
      <div class="inline-block text-xs font-bold text-teal-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">
        Assista em 1 minuto
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-4">
        Entenda o metodo <span class="text-gradient-teal">A.Z.U.L.</span> em menos de 1 min
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-navy-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Veja por que milhares de empreendedores trabalham demais e lucram de menos - e o que fazer pra virar esse jogo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-sm">
      <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl ring-4 ring-teal-500/30 bg-black" style="aspect-ratio: 9/16;">
        <iframe
          src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${VIDEO_ID}?rel=0&modestbranding=1&playsinline=1`}
          title="Negocio no Azul - Metodo A.Z.U.L."
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
          class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <a
        href="https://pay.hotmart.com/I105499750V?checkoutMode=2"
        data-cta="checkout"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-700 text-white font-bold font-display text-sm sm:text-base uppercase tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded-xl btn-glow hover:scale-105 transition-transform"
      >
        Quero sair do vermelho por R$ 97
        <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" /></svg>
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-navy-200 mt-3">
        <span class="line-through text-navy-300">R$ 447</span> hoje por <strong class="text-gold-400">R$ 97</strong> - 12x de R$ 9,90
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
